olid Book, and made it nobler than a thousand months. It is the night of gifts for the accepted and calamities for the rejected. Woe be upon those who return with Your Wrath and blessed be those who enjoy Your Mercy on that night.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ عَبْدِكَ وَرَسُوْلِكَ وَنَبِيِّكَ مُؤَدِّي الرِّسَالَةِ وَمُوْضِحِ الدَّلَالَةِ اَوْصَلَ كِتَابَكَ وَاسْتَحَقَّ ثَوَابَكَ وَاَنْهَجَ سَبِيْلَ حَلَالِكَ وَحَرَامِكَ وَكَشَفَ عَنْ شَعَاۗئِرِكَ وَاَعْلَامِكَ فَاِنَّ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةَ الَّتِيْ وَسَمْتَهَا بِالْقَدْرِ وَاَنْزَلْتَ فِيْهَا مُحْكَمَ الذِّكْرِ وَفَضَّلْتَهَا عَلٰى اَلْفِ شَهْرٍ وَهِيَ لَيْلَةُ مَوَاهِبِ الْمَقْبُوْلِيْنَ وَمَصَاۗئِبِ الْمَرْدُوْدِيْنَ فَيَا خُسْرَانَ مَنْ بَاۗءَ فِيْهَا بِسَخَطِهٖ وَيَا وَيْحَ مَنْ حُظِيَ فِيْهَا بِرَحْمَتِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "Arabi